title: Galeria Kaufhof Pokal Challenge
text: The Galeria Kaufhof Pokal Challenge was a <a href="golf">golf</a> tournament on the <a href="Challenge%20Tour">Challenge Tour</a> that was played at Golfclub Rittergut Birkhof in <a href="Korschenbroich">Korschenbroich</a>, <a href="Germany">Germany</a> from 2001 to 2005.
